{"tid":2406581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發！張建宗：圍封行動有效 過年後或再做！！","createTime":"2021-02-13T10:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T08:53:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"08fcaa7a2682c5a01f46d0f09c7fe145bbd2eb99","tid":2406581,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗指圍封行動有效，不排除視乎疫情，農曆新年後再做；又指若確診數字維持單位數，可以有條件恢復通關，不排除疫苗是其中一個考慮通關的條件。<br />\n<br />\n過去多日，全港多區的圍封行動確診比率百分之0.08。政務司司長張建宗強調，數字不低、有成效，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>形容措施是戰略調整，又不排除會再做。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/local/60278372335d19e64554d0ea/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E7%A8%B1%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88-%E8%A6%96%E4%B9%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E6%88%96%E5%86%8D%E5%81%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F60278372335d19e64554d0ea%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25B0%2581%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2595%2588-%25E8%25A6%2596%25E4%25B9%258E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2581%259A&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=7412178d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/local/60278372335d19e64554d0ea/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E7%A8%B1%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88-%E8%A6%96%E4%B9%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E6%88%96%E5%86%8D%E5%81%9A</a>"},{"pid":"ba7bbb2348a5eee6944b5a85b261ae170c4cc170","tid":2406581,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj